{"tid":659634,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世盃倒數36日】摩佬：C朗可領葡萄牙奪世界盃","createTime":"2018-05-10T04:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T09:51:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5083666ec1c55c181fd19542217137f535b4898d","tid":659634,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=3fHLkMD1HHb%2BTUAHXfv7rdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ceb5c155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】展望祖國葡萄牙的世界盃前景，曼聯領隊摩連奴直言基斯坦奴朗拿度可率大軍封王。<br />\n<br />\n作為2016歐洲國家盃冠軍，葡萄牙強勢出征俄羅斯世界盃，爭標機會回升，皆因大紅人基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）經過季初一輪低潮後，今季各項賽事已轟入42球。「葡萄牙的陣容很有趣，沒有C朗，一切免談；只要有他，不可能也是可能。」摩連奴對前弟子評價甚高，直言國家隊捧盃並非不可能。 「同一道理，阿根廷沒有美斯的話，爭標便成空談；有他的話，他們會是熱門之一。」不過，摩佬似乎較看好巴西：「相對而言，巴西的陣容最平衡，技術和心理上，他們既有天才球員，也有硬朗鐵漢，防守嚴密，前場有尼馬、菲臘比古天奴等，質素很高。」"},{"pid":"80f3247423cddc50cc2a86bf73745b548769b056","tid":659634,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f73f64e271d24950e0b03afbaf009736ec8fdc21","tid":659634,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80f3247423cddc50cc2a86bf73745b548769b056","tid":659634,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"弱智仔,尋日news咪36日囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87db64138e1102c09e02da46e6241c677f30998","tid":659634,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73f64e271d24950e0b03afbaf009736ec8fdc21","tid":659634,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"80f3247423cddc50cc2a86bf73745b548769b056","tid":659634,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"弱智仔,尋日news咪36日囉 <img src=\"/assets